00:01:38.540 --> 00:01:39.340 align:middle line:90%
ordinarily.

00:01:39.340 --> 00:01:40.140 align:middle line:90%
>> Right, yeah.

00:01:40.140 --> 00:01:42.910 align:middle line:84%
>> And if we say someone
is intelligent, it is.

00:01:42.910 --> 00:01:45.910 align:middle line:84%
So what we've done here
is brought two aspects

00:01:45.910 --> 00:01:50.230 align:middle line:84%
of our humanness together
that have been, in a way,

00:01:50.230 --> 00:01:52.270 align:middle line:90%
