supposed to be emotional.

00:01:59.750 --> 00:02:01.480 align:middle line:90%
And yet we are.

00:02:01.480 --> 00:02:03.280 align:middle line:84%
And the idea of
emotional intelligence

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:06.880 align:middle line:84%
means being intelligent
about our emotions,

00:02:06.880 --> 00:02:10.419 align:middle line:84%
knowing and understanding
them, and intelligent in how

00:02:10.419 --> 00:02:14.260 align:middle line:84%
we use them in our everyday
lives and in our businesses.

00:02:14.260 --> 00:02:18.440 align:middle line:84%
>> There's something there,
beginning to see how we learn

00:02:18.440 --> 00:02:19.240 align:middle line:90%
differently.

00:02:19.240 --> 00:02:21.550 align:middle line:84%
And emotional intelligence
has something to do with that,

00:02:21.550 --> 00:02:22.090 align:middle line:90%
doesn't it?

00:02:22.090 --> 00:02:23.140 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:02:23.140 --> 00:02:26.500 align:middle line:84%
