a sense of fear,

00:03:19.780 --> 00:03:23.540 align:middle line:84%
then I'm not going to
be able to integrate it.

00:03:23.540 --> 00:03:24.340 align:middle line:90%
>> Correct.

00:03:24.340 --> 00:03:26.380 align:middle line:84%
And if you work
for an organization

00:03:26.380 --> 00:03:31.720 align:middle line:84%
in which intimidation and fear
based management is the norm,

00:03:31.720 --> 00:03:34.330 align:middle line:84%
then there will be a
pervading sense of fear,

00:03:34.330 --> 00:03:37.810 align:middle line:84%
usually subconscious, throughout
the organization, which

00:03:37.810 --> 00:03:41.200 align:middle line:84%
inhibits creative thinking
and learning and growth

00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:42.880 align:middle line:90%
within the organization.

00:03:42.880 --> 00:03:46.810 align:middle line:84%
