00:03:46.810 --> 00:03:49.610 align:middle line:84%
their understanding of
emotional intelligence?

00:03:49.610 --> 00:03:51.250 align:middle line:84%
What have they
gained in their life?

00:03:51.250 --> 00:03:52.810 align:middle line:84%
What have they
learned about themself

00:03:52.810 --> 00:03:55.390 align:middle line:84%
and how has it
changed their life?

00:03:55.390 --> 00:03:58.690 align:middle line:84%
>> I think probably one of
the most profound impacts

00:03:58.690 --> 00:04:01.660 align:middle line:84%
of increased emotional
intelligence, Carolyn,

00:04:01.660 --> 00:04:06.820 align:middle line:84%
is intuition and a greater
sense of trust in one's own

00:04:06.820 --> 00:04:08.350 align:middle line:90%
intuition.

00:04:08.350 --> 00:04:11.710 align:middle line:10%
Intuition is the head and
the heart working together

00:04:11.710 --> 00:04:16.089 align:middle line:10%
to create a brilliant,
innovative idea about how

00:04:16.089 --> 00:04:18.260 align:middle line:10%
to handle this
personal situation,

00:04:18.260 --> 00:04:21.550 align:middle line:10%
or how to respond to
this business challenge.

00:04:21.550 --> 00:04:24.610 align:middle line:84%
Every great business
leader understands

00:04:24.610 --> 00:04:26.230 align:middle line:90%
the value of intuition.

00:04:26.230 --> 00:04:30.930 align:middle line:10%
We simply don't have enough
time to gather all of the facts.

00:04:30.930 --> 00:04:34.300 align:middle line:84%
And in some cases, the facts
are simply not available.

00:04:34.300 --> 00:04:37.480 align:middle line:10%
And so it is intuition
that gives us the ability

00:04:37.480 --> 00:04:41.470 align:middle line:10%
to move quickly and effectively
in situations which are perhaps

00:04:41.470 --> 00:04:43.570 align:middle line:10%
poorly defined.

00:04:43.570 --> 00:04:47.720 align:middle line:84%
>> So how is our intuition
and our emotional intelligence

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:48.610 align:middle line:90%
joined together?

00:04:48.610 --> 00:04:52.520 align:middle line:84%
What is-- deepen my
understanding in that area.

00:04:52.520 --> 00:04:55.710 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, intelligence
is about the intellect,

00:04:55.710 --> 00:04:58.240 align:middle line:84%
which is about the functioning
of certain components

00:04:58.240 --> 00:04:59.650 align:middle line:90%
of the brain.

00:04:59.650 --> 00:05:02.620 align:middle line:10%
And emotion has
more to do with what

00:05:02.620 --> 00:05:06.340 align:middle line:10%
we call the heart, the
metaphorical heart.

00:05:06.340 --> 00:05:09.400 align:middle line:84%
And that has to do
with the right brain

00:05:09.400 --> 00:05:11.110 align:middle line:84%
and the emotional
brain, which is

00:05:11.110 --> 00:05:15.190 align:middle line:84%
the mammalian and reptilian
aspects of the brain.

00:05:15.190 --> 00:05:17.920 align:middle line:84%
But you know, an interesting
kind of side comment

00:05:17.920 --> 00:05:21.680 align:middle line:84%
here is that the actual
physical organ of the heart--

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:25.330 align:middle line:84%
this is discovered by
HeartMath institute--

00:05:25.330 --> 00:05:27.970 align:middle line:84%
the physical organ
of the human heart

00:05:27.970 --> 00:05:32.250 align:middle line:84%
works better when we express
love and appreciation

00:05:32.250 --> 00:05:35.890 align:middle line:84%
and functions more poorly when
we are cynical and expressing

00:05:35.890 --> 00:05:37.210 align:middle line:90%
doubt and fear.

00:05:37.210 --> 00:05:38.630 align:middle line:90%
So that's an interesting thing.

00:05:38.630 --> 00:05:42.190 align:middle line:84%
The physical heart
wants us, likes it

00:05:42.190 --> 00:05:45.550 align:middle line:84%
when we are expressing
love and appreciation.

00:05:45.550 --> 00:05:47.562 align:middle line:84%
>> And feeling loved
and appreciated also.

00:05:47.562 --> 00:05:49.270 align:middle line:84%
Again, I'm thinking
that that's when we'd

00:05:49.270 --> 00:05:52.540 align:middle line:90%
be more receptive to learning.

00:05:52.540 --> 00:05:55.990 align:middle line:84%
Are there different levels
of emotional intelligence

00:05:55.990 --> 00:05:57.080 align:middle line:90%
with different people?

00:05:57.080 --> 00:05:57.880 align:middle line:10%
>> Absolutely.

00:05:57.880 --> 00:06:01.210 align:middle line:10%
There is an EQ map
that has been developed

00:06:01.210 --> 00:06:03.970 align:middle line:10%
by an organization
in San Francisco that

00:06:03.970 --> 00:06:09.190 align:middle line:10%
is a very user friendly
self-evaluation kind of way

00:06:09.190 --> 00:06:11.860 align:middle line:10%
of measuring emotional
intelligence that

00:06:11.860 --> 00:06:16.780 align:middle line:10%
points specifically and directly
to what we can do to raise it.

00:06:16.780 --> 00:06:19.900 align:middle line:84%
And so there are clearly
delineated processes

00:06:19.900 --> 00:06:24.490 align:middle line:84%
for measuring and for increasing
emotional intelligence that

00:06:24.490 --> 00:06:27.560 align:middle line:84%
can be applied in the personal
and professional dimensions.

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:31.220 align:middle line:84%
>> So we want to increase
our emotional intelligence.

00:06:31.220 --> 00:06:32.170 align:middle line:90%
>> Absolutely.

00:06:32.170 --> 00:06:34.690 align:middle line:84%
>> And what happens, what
are some of the, I guess,

00:06:34.690 --> 00:06:39.910 align:middle line:84%
the benefits that we derive
from having more awareness

00:06:39.910 --> 00:06:43.870 align:middle line:84%
and increased intelligence
about our emotions?

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:47.890 align:middle line:84%
>> One great benefit is an
improved ability to communicate

00:06:47.890 --> 00:06:54.010 align:middle line:84%
clearly and directly, and fewer
obstacles and barriers between

00:06:54.010 --> 00:06:56.650 align:middle line:84%
us and significant
people in our lives.

00:06:56.650 --> 00:07:00.880 align:middle line:84%
Whether those are business
associates or loved ones,

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:04.570 align:middle line:90%
family members, dear friends.

00:07:04.570 --> 00:07:08.380 align:middle line:10%
So barriers are removed
as clarity and precision

00:07:08.380 --> 00:07:11.110 align:middle line:10%
in communication is increased.

00:07:11.110 --> 00:07:12.800 align:middle line:90%
That's one area.

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:17.420 align:middle line:84%
Another area has to do with
adaptability and flexibility,

00:07:17.420 --> 00:07:19.630 align:middle line:84%
being able to move
quickly and effectively

00:07:19.630 --> 00:07:21.940 align:middle line:90%
through stressful situations.

00:07:21.940 --> 00:07:27.850 align:middle line:10%
Because it is anger and fear
and related feelings of feeling

00:07:27.850 --> 00:07:30.910 align:middle line:10%
paralyzed or stressed
out or overwhelmed that

00:07:30.910 --> 00:07:33.790 align:middle line:10%
slow us down or
even stop us cold

00:07:33.790 --> 00:07:36.240 align:middle line:10%
in those stressful situations.

00:07:36.240 --> 00:07:39.100 align:middle line:84%
The more at peace we
are and the more fluid

00:07:39.100 --> 00:07:42.010 align:middle line:84%
we are in how we are
managing our emotions,

00:07:42.010 --> 00:07:47.320 align:middle line:84%
the more effectively we can move
through stress and even crisis.

00:07:47.320 --> 00:07:52.300 align:middle line:84%
So crisis management
becomes much more easy

00:07:52.300 --> 00:07:54.770 align:middle line:84%
and flowing with
emotional intelligence.

00:07:54.770 --> 00:07:55.960 align:middle line:90%
>> Bill, give me an example.

00:07:55.960 --> 00:08:00.190 align:middle line:84%
Give us an example of
what managing our emotions

00:08:00.190 --> 00:08:04.420 align:middle line:84%
might look like, in either a
business or personal situation.

00:08:04.420 --> 00:08:07.220 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, it's first of
all an internal process.

00:08:07.220 --> 00:08:09.250 align:middle line:90%
It means I need to know myself.

00:08:09.250 --> 00:08:12.520 align:middle line:84%
And I need to know
how to respond when

00:08:12.520 --> 00:08:14.860 align:middle line:90%
I feel my emotions coming up.

00:08:14.860 --> 00:08:19.690 align:middle line:84%
If I am aware of some anger,
some fear, some sorrow that's

00:08:19.690 --> 00:08:22.810 align:middle line:84%
in me, knowing what
I can do about that,

00:08:22.810 --> 00:08:27.190 align:middle line:84%
not necessarily to eliminate
it, but to respond to it,

00:08:27.190 --> 00:08:31.750 align:middle line:84%
and perhaps to communicate
effectively from that emotion.

00:08:31.750 --> 00:08:33.460 align:middle line:10%
Because what we're
finding in business,

00:08:33.460 --> 00:08:36.429 align:middle line:10%
for example, is that if
you and I are in a business

00:08:36.429 --> 00:08:41.080 align:middle line:10%
relationship and I'm feeling
a particularly large amount

00:08:41.080 --> 00:08:42.429 align:middle line:10%
of sorrow today--

00:08:42.429 --> 00:08:45.730 align:middle line:10%
I may know some of the
reasons, I may not know them--

00:08:45.730 --> 00:08:49.720 align:middle line:10%
if I can talk to you briefly
about that before we begin

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:51.940 align:middle line:10%
any of our business
processes, we

00:08:51.940 --> 00:08:54.530 align:middle line:10%
will do much better business.

00:08:54.530 --> 00:08:57.740 align:middle line:84%
I will be more fully
in the relationship

00:08:57.740 --> 00:09:00.710 align:middle line:84%
and we will be more effective
in our business processes.

00:09:00.710 --> 00:09:02.210 align:middle line:90%
>> So what would you say?

00:09:02.210 --> 00:09:03.010 align:middle line:90%
We're sitting down.

00:09:03.010 --> 00:09:04.927 align:middle line:84%
There's a board meeting
that's about to start.

00:09:04.927 --> 00:09:07.330 align:middle line:84%
And you're across
the table from me.

00:09:07.330 --> 00:09:09.890 align:middle line:84%
What would be--
what would you say?

00:09:09.890 --> 00:09:11.650 align:middle line:84%
>> I would say, I'd
like you to know--

00:09:11.650 --> 00:09:14.920 align:middle line:84%
and let's say that the
whole group is here.

00:09:14.920 --> 00:09:18.420 align:middle line:10%
I'd like all of you to know that
I'm feeling some sadness today,

00:09:18.420 --> 00:09:20.560 align:middle line:10%
and I've got some ideas
of why that's there.

00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:22.660 align:middle line:10%
There's some
problems in my family

00:09:22.660 --> 00:09:26.050 align:middle line:10%
that I may talk with you
individually about later.

00:09:26.050 --> 00:09:30.700 align:middle line:84%
And also, there's some of this
that I'm not quite sure about.

00:09:30.700 --> 00:09:33.700 align:middle line:10%
Perhaps I'll learn more
as the day goes on.

00:09:33.700 --> 00:09:35.500 align:middle line:84%
But I wanted you
to know that this

00:09:35.500 --> 00:09:36.830 align:middle line:90%
is what's going on with me.

00:09:36.830 --> 00:09:40.510 align:middle line:10%
And it's not about you
or our subject matter.

00:09:40.510 --> 00:09:42.490 align:middle line:84%
This is who I am today
and this is what I'm

00:09:42.490 --> 00:09:44.950 align:middle line:90%
bringing into this situation.

00:09:44.950 --> 00:09:48.040 align:middle line:84%
>> And I would suspect
as a result then,

00:09:48.040 --> 00:09:49.360 align:middle line:90%
it wouldn't come up.

00:09:49.360 --> 00:09:50.380 align:middle line:90%
It would be managed.

00:09:50.380 --> 00:09:53.530 align:middle line:84%
It wouldn't come up in
a different way, maybe

00:09:53.530 --> 00:09:57.370 align:middle line:84%
a fearful way or something, when
a subject matter is brought up

00:09:57.370 --> 00:10:01.060 align:middle line:84%
at the business meeting that has
nothing to do with your sorrow.

00:10:01.060 --> 00:10:03.850 align:middle line:84%
But somehow, your sorrow
would enter into that.

00:10:03.850 --> 00:10:04.720 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:06.760 align:middle line:10%
And to play this out
a little further,

00:10:06.760 --> 00:10:08.710 align:middle line:10%
let's say we have some
important business

00:10:08.710 --> 00:10:10.450 align:middle line:10%
decisions to make today.

00:10:10.450 --> 00:10:12.130 align:middle line:90%
And this is how I feel.

00:10:12.130 --> 00:10:16.570 align:middle line:84%
Fear and anger can immediately
be triggered by this feeling

00:10:16.570 --> 00:10:17.710 align:middle line:90%
that I'm having.

00:10:17.710 --> 00:10:20.080 align:middle line:84%
If I'm not aware of it
and in touch with it

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:23.260 align:middle line:84%
and I haven't come
clear with the group

00:10:23.260 --> 00:10:28.150 align:middle line:84%
and really presented myself, who
I am and how I feel, then one,

00:10:28.150 --> 00:10:31.670 align:middle line:84%
my decision making will be
affected by my emotions.

00:10:31.670 --> 00:10:35.350 align:middle line:84%
I will be too fearful and
perhaps pass on a good business

00:10:35.350 --> 00:10:38.410 align:middle line:84%
opportunity, based
on a personal emotion

00:10:38.410 --> 00:10:39.690 align:middle line:90%
that I'm not in touch with.

00:10:39.690 --> 00:10:41.290 align:middle line:84%
>> It would be
blocked, in some way.

00:10:41.290 --> 00:10:42.207 align:middle line:90%
>> I would be blocked.

00:10:42.207 --> 00:10:44.290 align:middle line:10%
And you, and other
board members,

00:10:44.290 --> 00:10:48.700 align:middle line:10%
might misinterpret my
affect, the feeling

00:10:48.700 --> 00:10:53.470 align:middle line:10%
that I put into what I
say, as related to them

00:10:53.470 --> 00:10:55.420 align:middle line:10%
or related to the
business, when it really

00:10:55.420 --> 00:10:59.410 align:middle line:10%
has nothing to do with
what's going on at the table.

00:10:59.410 --> 00:11:04.360 align:middle line:84%
>> And you expect me, then,
to not have a long response,

00:11:04.360 --> 00:11:07.780 align:middle line:84%
but at least to
acknowledge where you are.

00:11:07.780 --> 00:11:10.330 align:middle line:84%
And then we can
kind of pave the way

00:11:10.330 --> 00:11:12.490 align:middle line:90%
to have a good business meeting.

00:11:12.490 --> 00:11:15.003 align:middle line:84%
When we come back-- we
need to take a moment

00:11:15.003 --> 00:11:17.170 align:middle line:84%
to hear from our supporters--
and when we come back,

00:11:17.170 --> 00:11:18.790 align:middle line:84%
let's talk a little
bit more about how

00:11:18.790 --> 00:11:22.000 align:middle line:84%
this also, the awareness
of emotional intelligence

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:25.263 align:middle line:84%
affects our personal
life, as well.

00:11:25.263 --> 00:11:26.680 align:middle line:84%
You're watching
"World of Wisdom."

00:11:26.680 --> 00:11:27.550 align:middle line:90%
I'm Carolyn Craft.

00:11:27.550 --> 00:11:29.310 align:middle line:84%
